import React, { Fragment } from "react"; import { connect } from "react-redux" import { createStructuredSelector } from "reselect" import selectCartItems from "../../redux/cart/selectors/cart-items.selector.js" import cartTotal from "../../redux/cart/selectors/cart-total.selector.js" import "./checkout.scss" const CheckOut = ({ cartItems, total }) => { console.log(cartItems) return (
Product
Description
Quantity
Price
Remove
{ cartItems.map(cartItem => cartItem.name ) }
${total}
) } const mapStateToProps = createStructuredSelector({ cartItems: selectCartItems, total: cartTotal }) export default connect(mapStateToProps)(CheckOut);
